    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it's complicated, but \"depends on how you define progress\" feels like a bit of an easy way out. if you look at the actual outcomes, isn't there a clear trend where the push for inclusivity is actually just creating a climate where people are afraid to speak their minds? like, isn't the censorship aspect becoming the more dominant reality?",
